{"article_id":"NOJqPdWJq8aetwqC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On the morning after the partial government shutdown ended ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump said","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"talks with congressional Democrats over border security measures \" will start immediately , \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"but warned","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that it \" will not be easy \" to reach a compromise within the next three weeks .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"\" 21 days goes very quickly , \"","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"the president wrote on Twitter Saturday .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"\" Negotiations with Democrats will start immediately .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Will not be easy to make a deal ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"both parties very dug in .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The case for National Security has been greatly enhanced by what has been happening at the Border & through dialogue .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"We will build the Wall ! \"","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Trump on Friday evening signed a bill","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"to fund the government until Feb. 15 ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"ending the longest shutdown in U.S. history .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"The measure did not allocate taxpayer dollars to his campaign trail promise of a wall along the southern border ,","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"but Trump has pledged to secure that money in upcoming talks with House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"( D-Calif. )","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"( D-N.Y. ) .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"The president signaled Saturday","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"that he plans to seize upon a new caravan of Central American migrants","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"approaching the U.S.-Mexico border","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"as justification for his wall ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"tweeting :","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"\" If we had a powerful Wall ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"they wouldn ' t even try to make the long and dangerous journey .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Build the Wall","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"and Crime will Fall ! \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Trump had tweeted seven times before 10 a.m . ET ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"including five times on border security ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"once on Roger Stone","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"being indicted for lying to Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and another on the RNC","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"pledging support for the president in 2020 .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Later Saturday he tweeted :","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"`` Only fools , or people with a political agenda , don ' t want a Wall or Steel Barrier","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to protect our Country from Crime , Drugs and Human Trafficking .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"It will happen -","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"it always does ! ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Late Friday , the president had tweeted :","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"`` I wish","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"people would read or listen to my words on the Border Wall .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"This was in no way a concession .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"It was taking care of millions of people","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"who were getting badly hurt by the Shutdown","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"with the understanding","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that in 21 days ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"if no deal is done ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"it ' s off to the races ! ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":61,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":0,"right":60,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":60,"left":53,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":51,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":52,"left":3,"ri